</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="02DISA012" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-1C874C66-3A17-4AC4-886B-753A1A37D196.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 Open the ink system (todo)?>02 Open the ink system</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the rear top cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="02DISA014" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-44A21941-A21F-4C37-A066-3CEA7BE54DAA.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 How to remove the rear top cover of the ink system...?>02 How to remove the rear top cover of the ink system</xref>. 
