</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check the routing of the ink tubes for all ink tubes (C, M, Y, K and W). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Check if the ink tubes are all well connected to each other. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Indication: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The hose coming from the lower pump is not in any small holder. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">If you see a hose from a lower pump in a holder, please correct the routing as indicated.</b> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The circles indicate the tube connections. Double check if the tubes are correctly connected to each other. 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "> Check the routing of the ink tubes for all ink tubes (C, M, Y, K and W). 
